articles.author: Noah Robertson
articles.title: US strikes 75 ISIS targets in Syria after Assad regime collapses - Military Times
articles.description: The strikes come as America's presence in the country is increasingly in doubt.
articles.content:
SIMI VALLEY, Calif. American forces in the Middle East pounded central Syria Sunday in a massive round of strikes just a day after the countrys government crumbled.
